    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the<strong> pulled chicken</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>shredded harissa chicken</strong></p>",
