    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>shredded harissa chicken</strong> over the<strong> crunchy pitta salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the<strong> lemony dressing</strong> and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped mint </strong>and<strong> dill</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
